@startuml
robust "Robust Player" as R
concise "Concise Player" as C
clock "Clock Signal" as clk with period 10
binary "Binary Signal" as B
analog "Analog Signal" between 0 and 10 as A
rectangle "Rectangle Player" as Rect

@0
R is StateA
C is Waiting
B is low
A is 0
Rect is Init

@20
R is StateB
C is Active
B is high
A is 7.5
Rect is Done
@enduml
